Login test cases

Case #1. Sign In - Empty fields
1. Go to https://qa-complex-app-for-testing.herokuapp.com/
2. Push the button "Sign In" .//button[text()='Sign In']

find allert .//div[text()='Invalid username / password']
find Sign In button .//button[text()='Sign In']

Case #2. Sign In - Error
1. Go to https://qa-complex-app-for-testing.herokuapp.com/
2. Enter random name to Username field .//input[@name='username']
3. Enter random to Password field .//input[@name='password']
4. Push the button "Sign In" .//button[text()='Sign In']

find allert .//div[text()='Invalid username / password']
find Sign In button .//button[text()='Sign In']

Case #3. Sign up
1. Go to https://qa-complex-app-for-testing.herokuapp.com/
2. Enter random name to Username field .//input[@id='username-register']
3. Save value name for the future*
4. Enter random email to Email field .//input[@id='email-register']
5. Enter random password to Password field .//input[@id='password-register']
6. Save value password for the future*
7. Push the button "Sign up for OurApp" .//button[text()="Sign up for OurApp"]

find name in .//span[@class='text-white mr-2']
find name in .//strong
finf Sign Out button .//button[text()='Sign Out']

Case #4. Sign In
1. Go to https://qa-complex-app-for-testing.herokuapp.com/
2. Enter name to Username field .//input[@name='username']
3. Enter password to Password field .//input[@name='password']
4. Push the button "Sign In" .//button[text()='Sign In']

find name in .//span[@class='text-white mr-2']
find name in .//strong
finf Sign Out button .//button[text()='Sign Out']

Case #5. Sign out
1. Go to https://qa-complex-app-for-testing.herokuapp.com/
2. Enter name to Username field .//input[@name='username']
3. Enter password to Password field .//input[@name='password']
4. Push the button "Sign in" .//button[text()='Sign In']
5. Push Sign Out button .//button[text()='Sign Out']

find Sign In button .//button[text()='Sign In']
